  After Effects 101

In this video, I'm going to give you a quick tour of one of my favorite creative tools, Adobe After Effects. After Effects is a 2.5D compositing software that is used for quick FX and compositing in the filmmaking world. It's much easier to use than other high-end software and can do everything from motion design to VFX.

This will be a quick overview for anyone new to the software. But if you are more experienced with the tool, you can totally skip this video.
